Beornulf<br>
51 Champion / Bristlebane <p><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=91376"><img src="http://www.snigel.org/klumhru/klumhru.jpg" border="0"></a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ufirion69.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Firion69</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(10/25/01 3:25:59 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=184.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Specs and Death</span><hr size=1> Note for kiting the bloodgills: For pulling all 4, just take another pullinground, simple as that. <br>
Pull one at pillar, swim to under platform, flux, hit the water and outrun the two following you, swim down to pillar flux gobbo swim to other pillar flux the last gobbo, run to beach, kill.<br>
(Done with swim skill maxed or close to maxed tho, if its not maxed they catch you in the water)<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=rolfe>rolfe</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(11/12/01 12:29:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=184.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Specs and Death</span><hr size=1> I think the genius is the gal that missed the sarcasm in rashakra's story.  He wasn't saying that killing newbies is fun OR funny.  What he DID say was that his story had a moral, and that moral amounted to staying AWAY from newbies when killing specs.<br>
<br>
It was a good story, Rashakra.<br>
